\v 2 sikhangele kuJesu umqalisi lomphelelisi wokholo \add lwethu\x + 1 Kor. 1.8.\x*\add*, owathi\x + Luka 24.26. 1 Pet. 1.11.\x* ngenxa yentokozo\x + Mat. 25.21,23.\x* ayimiselweyo\x + 6.18.\x*, waqinisela esiphambanweni\x + Fil. 2.8.\x*, edelela ihlazo\x + Hlab. 69.19.\x*, wahlala\x + 1.3. & Seb. 2.33.\x* ngakwesokunene sesihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu.
