\v 4 Kalikamelani la\add kho\add* kuze kube segazini\x + 10.32-34. 1 Kor. 10.13.\x* lisilwa lesono;
\v 5 njalo selikhohliwe inkuthazo\x + 13.22. Seb. 13.15.\x*, ekhuluma kini njengemadodaneni \add eyokuthi\add*: Ndodana yami\x + Zaga 3.11,12.\x*, ungadeleli ukulaya kweNkosi, njalo ungapheli amandla\x + 11.5. Gal. 6.9.\x*, nxa usolwa yiyo;
