\v 7 Uba likhuthazela ekulayweni, uNkulunkulu uyaliphatha njengamadodana\x + Dute. 8.5. & Zaga 13.24. Tshu. 9.1.\x*; ngoba yiyiphi indodana uyise angayilayiyo\x + 1 Kor. 11.32.\x*?
\v 8 Kodwa uba lingelakulaywa, okuthi bonke bangabahlanganyeli bakho\x + 1 Pet. 5.9.\x*, ngakho lingabokufetshwa njalo kalisiwo amadodana.
