\v 10 Ngoba bona kambe ba\add si\add*laya okwensuku ezinlutshwana, njengokubona kwabo; kodwa yena kube yikusizakala \add kwethu\add*, ukuze \add si\add*hlanganyele ubungcwele bakhe\x + 2 Pet. 1.4. Levi 11.44.\x*.
\v 11 Lakho konke ukulaywa okukhona kakubonakali angathi ngokwentokozo, kodwa ngokosizi; emva kwalokho-ke kuyabalethela isithelo\x + Jak. 3.17,18.\x* sokuthula sokulunga abaqeqetshwa ngakho\x + 5.14.\x*.
