\v 13 njalo lenzele inyawo zenu\x + Zaga 4.26.\x* indlela eziqondileyo, ukuze okuqhulayo kungenyeli\x + Zaga 4.27.\x*, kodwa kulalokho kusiliswe\x + Jak. 5.16. Gal. 6.1.\x*.
\v 14 Nxwanelani ukuthula\x + Roma 14.19.\x* labo bonke, lobungcwele\x + 1 Thes. 4.3.\x*, ngaphandle kwalokho kakulamuntu ozayibona iNkosi\x + Mat. 5.8. 2 Kor. 7.1. Efe. 5.5.\x*;
\v 15 liqaphelisa ukuze kungabi khona osilelayo\x + 2 Kor. 6.1. Gal. 5.4.\x* emuseni kaNkulunkulu\x + Seb. 13.43.\x*; kungamili lampande\x + Dute. 29.18.\x* yokubaba ikhathaze, njalo ngayo abanengi bangcoliswe;
\v 16 kakungabi lamuntu oyisifebe\x + 13.4.\x* kumbe ongakhonzi uNkulunkulu\x + 1 Tim. 1.9. 1 Tim. 1.9.\x*, njengoEsawu, owathengisa ubuzibulo bakhe\x + Gen. 25.33.\x* ngokudla okukodwa.
\v 17 Ngoba liyazi ukuthi lemva kwalokho, esethanda ukudla ilifa\x + Gen. 27.34,36,38.\x* lesibusiso, waliwa; ngoba kayitholanga indawo yokuphenduka\x + 6.6.\x*, lanxa wayidingisisa ngezinyembezi\x + 11.6.\x*.
\s Intaba yeSinayi leyeZiyoni
\p
\v 18 Ngoba kalizanga entabeni\x + Eks. 19.12,18,19; 20.18. Dute. 4.11; 5.22. 2 Kor. 3.9.\x* engathintwa, lemlilweni ovuthayo, lekufiphaleni, lemnyameni, lesivunguvungwini,
\v 19 lekukhaleni kophondo\x + Eks. 19.16.\x*, lelizwini lamazwi\x + 12.26.\x*, okwathi labo abezwayo\x + Eks. 20.19.\x* bancenga ukuthi kungabe kusa\add khulunywa\add* ilizwi kubo;
\v 20 ngoba babengelakukumela lokho okwalaywayo \add ukuthi\add*: Ngitsho lenyamazana uba ithinta intaba\x + Eks. 19.12,13.\x*, izakhandwa ngamatshe, kumbe itshokwe ngomtshoko;
\v 21 njalo, kwakusesabeka kangaka\x + Eks. 19.16. Roma 8.15.\x* lokho okwabonwayo, uMozisi wathi: Ngilovalo, ngiyathuthumela.
\v 22 Kodwa lize entabeni iSiyoni\x + Isam. 14.1.\x*, lemzini\x + 11.10,16; 13.14. Efe. 2.19. Fil. 3.20.\x* kaNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + Hlab. 42.2.\x*, eJerusalema yasezulwini\x + Gal. 4.26.\x*, lakuzigidi zengilosi ezingelakubalwa\x + 1 Kho. 22.19.\x*\x + Juda 1.14. Isam. 5.11.\x*,
