\v 25 Qaphelani ukuthi lingamali okhulumayo. Ngoba uba bengaphephanga\x + 2.3.\x* labo abala\x + 3.17.\x* lowo owakhuluma okuvela kuNkulunkulu emhlabeni\x + 8.5.\x*, kakhulu kangakanani thina esimfulathelayo lowo \add okhuluma\add* evela emazulwini;
\v 26 olizwi lakhe\x + 12.19.\x* ngalesosikhathi lanyikinya umhlaba, kodwa khathesi uthembisile, wathi: Ngi\add za\add*phinda kanye\x + Hag. 2.6.\x* ukunyikinya kungeyisiwo umhlaba wodwa, kodwa lezulu.
\v 27 Lalokhu \add ukuthi:\add* \add Ngiza\add*phinda kanye, kutshengisa ukususwa kwezinto ezinyikinywayo\x + Hlab. 102.26.\x*, kungathi ezenziweyo, ukuze kusale izinto ezinganyikinywayo.
\v 28 Ngakho njengoba sisemukela umbuso ongelakunyikinyekiswa, asibe\f + \fk asibe lomusa: \fl kumbe, \fq asibambe umusa.\f* lomusa esingamkhonza uNkulunkulu\x + Seb. 27.23.\x* ngawo ngokwemukelekayo\x + 13.21.\x* kanye lokuthobeka lokwesaba uNkulunkulu\x + 5.7.\x*;
